{{else}}

{{#system~}}
- **Offering (available / provided):**
```
{{#if not IsEmpty(text=current_products_and_services)}}{{current_products_and_services}}{{else}}null{{/if}}
```
- **Not offering (not available / not provided):**
```
{{#if not IsEmpty(text=current_products_and_services_not_offering)}}{{current_products_and_services_not_offering}}{{else}}null{{/if}}
```
